# Warning
This script copys the entire contents of the backup each time it is run so
havey traffic can accure.

# INSTALL
Open the main file and configure the first section. Run normally. Add to cron.

You will need:
List of folders to backup
Temporary folder to store temporary files
Location to store backups

# Decryption howto:
Create file /usr/local/bin/decrypt with the folowing lines (dont add the comment #)

---- cut here ----
#!/bin/bash
openssl des3 -d -a -in $1 -out ${1%.des3}
---- cut here ----

Usage:
decrypt example.tar.gz.des3

tar -xzf example.tar.gz

